OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FJudge agrees to reduce     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FTrump fraud bond to $175m  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A judge in New York has granted Donald 
OL,6, Trump's request to pause his $464m     
OL,7, civil fraud judgement, giving him 10   
OL,8, days to put up a reduced sum of $175m. 
OL,10,FThe former president's legal team had  
OL,11,Fpreviously said he was unable to secure
OL,12,Fa bond from a private company for      
OL,13,F$464m.                                 
OL,15,FHe had faced a deadline of Monday to   
OL,16,Fput up the bond or pay the full amount.
OL,18,FMr Trump was found liable earlier this 
OL,19,Fyear for repeatedly inflating the value
OL,20,Fof his assets.                         
